data.description: Located in the sought-after Signal Hill School District, this delightful cottage home features 3 beds, 2 baths, a detached garage, and a spacious full basement. The main level boasts wood floors, arched doorways, and a cozy masonry fireplace with a mantle. Natural light fills the separate dining area, while the updated kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances. The master suite includes a lovely bathroom and a charming reading nook. Outside, the property offers a covered porch, fenced yard, and firepit for outdoor relaxation. Quick interstate access makes commutes to Scott Air Force Base and downtown St. Louis a breeze. Don't pass up the chance to see this welcoming home - schedule your showing today! Occupancy status: PASSED.
